# This file defines who is responsible for reviewing changes to each part
# of this repository. Reviewers are automatically requested when a PR
# modifies files matching their pattern.
#
# Format: <pattern> <owner> [<owner> ...]
# Owners can be GitHub teams or individual usernames.
# The last matching pattern takes precedence.
#
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

